    <note>Fan(2) Zhi [8041] His ancestors were Gaoping jun Fan(2). Min's [577] father, Gao's [7024] uncle. His great granddaughter, whose maternal grandfather was Wang(2) Dan [8153], was Han(1) Jiang's [636] wife and Han(1) Zongshi's [662] mother. Her son-in-law was her brother's son, Shen [3286]. Zhi was the father-in-law of Cui(1) Zunlong. Wudai jiangxiang dachen nianbiao (ESWSBB). CBD, 2, 1634-5. Xian's [1678] son, Zunyong [3884]. His grandson, Fan(2) Yisun [3280], was the son-in-law of Li(2) Chuyun [8073]. Liu Ban, WJ, 39.2a; Yang Yi, WJ, 9.2b. CBD, 2, 1634-5.From Hartwell's ACTIVITY table:950:  Apt. Shumi fushi (State Council)951:  Promoted to Tong Zhongshu menxia Pingzhang shi (an office he held until Song) 《唐代人物知識ベース》記其生卒年為：911 - 964.</note>
